MBOMBELA – Load-shedding stage 2 will be implemented from 16:00 to 23:00 “to stabilise the system”. In Mbombela, the Delta area as well as West Acres, Macadamia and Halls will be affected from 17:00 to 19:30. Riverside Precinct will be affected from 21:00 until 23:30. ALSO READ: Things to consider if you want to make your life more fun